Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.09,0:03:23.40,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}M.I.N.A.M.I.K.E Let's Go！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.90,0:00:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.06,0:03:29.86,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(700,310)}現在、開始戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.90,0:00:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.39,0:03:40.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保阪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.60,0:03:42.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香好像喜歡看電影喲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.68,0:03:43.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.44,0:03:50.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  說到高中生健康地約會內容就是電影了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.75,0:03:53.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以和女兒們一起享受電影
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.45,0:03:57.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是  南春香喜歡什麼樣的電影？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.65,0:03:58.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.79,0:04:01.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過約會的話  愛情片不是板上釘釘的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.41,0:04:04.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊  愛情片嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.75,0:04:08.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛進行時這部愛情片似乎相當催淚喲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.26,0:04:10.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,催淚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.51,0:04:11.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼甜怎麼搞的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.91,0:04:13.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆米花不應該是咸的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.99,0:04:14.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是邪門歪道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.95,0:04:18.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電影院裏焦糖味才是王道  蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.77,0:04:20.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼你這是只喜歡甜食的小鬼的味覺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.79,0:04:21.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.42,0:04:27.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著我  南春香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.90,0:04:30.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的淚水由我來擦去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.95,0:04:35.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只要為我拭去汗水就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.08,0:04:43.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏樹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.01,0:04:47.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.38,0:04:49.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏樹  喜歡電影什麼的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.17,0:04:52.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電影什麼的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.45,0:04:54.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比較喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.22,0:04:55.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.74,0:04:58.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是別人送的  方便的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.22,0:05:02.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電影票啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.01,0:05:04.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.73,0:05:05.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.05,0:05:08.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想作為之前烤肉的回禮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.34,0:05:10.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.25,0:05:14.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香學姐邀我去看電影
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.38,0:05:17.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛進行時
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.89,0:05:19.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼樣的電影啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.66,0:05:20.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.09,0:05:23.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁美相當喜歡看電影對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.81,0:05:24.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.12,0:05:26.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看戀愛進行時吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.68,0:05:28.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是個什麼樣的電影來著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.42,0:05:31.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  聽說是相當催淚的愛情片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.17,0:05:34.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.69,0:05:37.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎  是催淚的愛情片嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.96,0:05:39.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.77,0:05:40.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這張票…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.25,0:05:44.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是接連不斷命運的巧合下兩人墜入愛河的電影
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.40,0:05:47.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我這樣的可喜歡這類電影了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.55,0:05:49.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對這種電影沒興趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.99,0:05:52.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我周圍的人都這麼說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.36,0:05:54.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我再去問問別人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.40,0:06:00.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏樹的那個眼神是非常悲傷的眼神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.06,0:06:02.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  夏樹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.88,0:06:03.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.71,0:06:05.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了什麼悲傷的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.25,0:06:08.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是什麼悲傷的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.57,0:06:09.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個  仁美
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.91,0:06:11.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡電影嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.81,0:06:14.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  算是…比較喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.31,0:06:17.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方便的話…怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.26,0:06:21.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電影票
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.47,0:06:24.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.00,0:06:25.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.12,0:06:26.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.47,0:06:29.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  被邀請去看電影了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.93,0:06:32.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被…被…被誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.22,0:06:34.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被誰邀請不重要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.02,0:06:36.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.19,0:06:38.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛進行時啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.32,0:06:39.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超認真的愛情片喲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.70,0:06:43.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是相當讓人笑不出來的戀愛故事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.53,0:06:45.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方的確認真過頭了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.06,0:06:46.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.59,0:06:50.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩張票疊在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.05,0:06:53.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊那傢伙真是個奇怪的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.69,0:06:54.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邀請別人的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.87,0:06:58.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該給別人一張自己留一張吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.39,0:07:00.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這並不是被邀請
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.77,0:07:03.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是讓她去邀請別人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.97,0:07:05.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.41,0:07:08.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露出了相當悲傷的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.21,0:07:10.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲傷的眼神？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.40,0:07:16.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方也是從中意的女生那裏拿到了這電影票吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.92,0:07:18.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.79,0:07:21.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁美你來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.72,0:07:23.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.69,0:07:27.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個煎餅  帶一點點咸味非常好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.70,0:07:31.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  那個票子春香姐姐不是也有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.56,0:07:37.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶  帶一點點咸味真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.90,0:00:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.64,0:07:40.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Spicy
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.50,0:07:41.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tabasco
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.62,0:07:42.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.28,0:07:44.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Spicyman
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.54,0:07:48.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好辣！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.48,0:07:52.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家三姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.90,0:00:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.22,0:07:58.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  還沒有去邀請嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.08,0:08:03.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邀請給我票子的人去看電影算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.74,0:08:05.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.63,0:08:11.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是為什麼把票子給我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.79,0:08:14.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人心什麼的不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.47,0:08:18.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  那麼來問男孩子這個問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.15,0:08:20.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏只有女孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.96,0:08:22.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問健
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.95,0:08:24.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是作罷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.42,0:08:25.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.64,0:08:32.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.00,0:08:34.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  南同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.03,0:08:35.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想問我什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.87,0:08:42.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  你們二人認識嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.48,0:08:44.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.81,0:08:46.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在拐角轉彎的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.03,0:08:49.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在買飲料的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.77,0:08:54.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是接連不斷命運的巧合下兩人墜入愛河的模式啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.62,0:08:55.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛進行時啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.14,0:08:59.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在抱歉  我對比我小的沒興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.39,0:09:01.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒有那個打算！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.42,0:09:04.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話  用不著問藤岡的男人心了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.58,0:09:08.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出於偶然原因這裏有兩張電影票
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.41,0:09:10.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣只能由你們兩個去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.81,0:09:12.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這樣啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.44,0:09:13.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同步了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.93,0:09:22.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行動驚人地同步啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.02,0:09:25.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別模仿我啊  羞死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.76,0:09:26.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是我要說的！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.14,0:09:29.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了算了  冷靜些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.63,0:09:31.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來喝杯茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.80,0:09:33.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同步成這樣真是佩服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.01,0:09:35.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.24,0:09:38.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想給這種現象取名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.70,0:09:40.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是不能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.40,0:09:41.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BINGO的話怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.93,0:09:43.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一般
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.71,0:09:45.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼合拍怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.25,0:09:46.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.23,0:09:57.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8次合拍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.24,0:09:58.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刷新最高紀錄了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.05,0:09:59.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去下廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.87,0:10:00.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.43,0:10:01.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你夠了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.16,0:10:05.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家的廁所只有一個所以請按順序來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.77,0:10:07.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  用猜拳決定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.05,0:10:09.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.08,0:10:10.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會出現嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.21,0:10:12.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剪刀石頭布
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.63,0:10:13.43,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.23,0:10:14.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剪刀石頭布
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.83,0:10:15.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剪刀石頭布
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.13,0:10:16.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剪刀石頭布
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.76,0:10:18.01,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同步率真高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.19,0:10:17.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剪刀石頭布
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.19,0:10:18.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剪刀石頭布
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.22,0:10:19.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剪刀石頭布
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.40,0:10:20.11,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會更新紀錄嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.67,0:10:23.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剪刀石頭～布！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.03,0:10:25.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經數不清了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.73,0:10:27.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉尼斯紀錄了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.35,0:10:30.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.69,0:10:31.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同步了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.19,0:10:33.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.29,0:10:35.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣永遠也決定不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.82,0:10:37.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要勉強你先去啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.07,0:10:38.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忍得住麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.81,0:10:41.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比忍耐力我可不會輸啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.95,0:10:43.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.76,0:10:46.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公共廁所的話附近是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.94,0:10:49.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  我的雙腳可以以馬赫的速度奔去那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.34,0:10:51.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是超馬赫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.35,0:10:52.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一決勝負吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.62,0:10:54.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.01,0:10:58.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.90,0:00:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.97,0:10:59.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,200)}南家鬥惡龍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.97,0:10:59.93,title1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,500)}終於抵達魔王之城  篇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.04,0:11:04.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,200)}南家鬥惡龍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.04,0:11:04.93,title1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,500)}充滿岩漿的地下  篇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.90,0:00:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.94,0:11:11.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.20,0:11:13.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是勝負如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.21,0:11:15.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時到達
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.94,0:11:16.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.09,0:11:20.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真行啊  你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.60,0:11:22.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  你才是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.47,0:11:23.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萌發友情了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.09,0:11:26.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成戀愛的話就是戀愛進行時的模式了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.58,0:11:27.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說不是啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.94,0:11:28.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛進行時？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.55,0:11:31.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去看戀愛進行時啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:34.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛的超催淚作不是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.96,0:11:38.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然有想看那個相當不好笑作品的稀有女性存在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.01,0:11:41.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出於偶然原因這裏有兩張電影票
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.49,0:11:43.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.15,0:11:44.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說這個是我的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.52,0:11:49.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來想阻止你一個人去看的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.66,0:11:50.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.77,0:11:54.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且這種愛情片應該是男女約會時看的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.57,0:11:56.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約會…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.76,0:12:01.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？藤岡有喜歡的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.26,0:12:03.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然的了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.96,0:12:06.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中學生總會有那麼一兩個喜歡的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.73,0:12:08.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能有兩個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.70,0:12:09.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是三個了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.70,0:12:17.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過藤岡看起來不太擅長向對方表白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.69,0:12:19.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊…也還…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.17,0:12:22.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.29,0:12:22.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合拍了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.34,0:12:25.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱們都不容易呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.22,0:12:26.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.41,0:12:27.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真不容易啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.23,0:12:32.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.26,0:12:37.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為男生應該努力去表達自己的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.82,0:12:41.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  我也認為表白是男生的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.80,0:12:52.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但即使我想表白也沒法完全傳達到…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.16,0:12:54.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者說其實我已經表白了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.55,0:12:57.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是表達方式的問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.20,0:12:59.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表達方式有問題呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.62,0:13:04.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼仁美理想中的表白是怎麼樣的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.02,0:13:06.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  我？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.20,0:13:08.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.81,0:13:09.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤岡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.85,0:13:11.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我仔細聽著好作為參考
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.88,0:13:12.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.23,0:13:16.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是想讓對方直接說  我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.91,0:13:22.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後再被一把抱住！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.47,0:13:27.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的…我會參考的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.68,0:13:34.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬馬這傢伙  整天不幫忙家務
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.76,0:13:35.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說了也不聽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.13,0:13:46.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎樣才能把我的想法跟她說清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.13,0:13:48.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏樹的那個眼神…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.91,0:13:51.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在煩惱怎樣才能傳達想法的眼神！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.66,0:13:54.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏樹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.10,0:13:58.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你在煩惱該如何傳達自己的想法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.56,0:14:02.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  果然不揍一頓是不會明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.50,0:14:03.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揍？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.01,0:14:08.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會讓我這麼做的  就只有你一個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.74,0:14:13.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太激烈太極端了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.10,0:14:14.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.78,0:14:18.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了  就沒有更溫柔些的方法了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.90,0:14:22.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你是怎樣來傳達自己的想法的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.49,0:14:24.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.30,0:14:32.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是那種等別人自己發現的類型啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.72,0:14:33.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.13,0:14:35.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只是等嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.61,0:14:40.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…比如說在那個人的旁邊走來走去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.46,0:14:41.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在旁邊走來走去？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.98,0:14:45.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.58,0:14:47.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在四目交接時…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.67,0:14:55.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就…就覺得心意已經傳達到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.71,0:15:00.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是對方還不明白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.72,0:15:08.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就大聲說  我喜歡你！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.05,0:15:12.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.61,0:15:16.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的…實際上我並沒有說過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.10,0:15:24.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才開始就在我旁邊轉來轉去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.31,0:15:34.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四目交接了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.59,0:15:37.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼嘛  有什麼想說的就直說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.51,0:15:39.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了  冬馬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.18,0:15:45.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜…喜…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.39,0:15:51.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種話怎麼可能說得出口！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.26,0:15:56.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底想幹什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.90,0:00:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.14,0:15:59.10,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,480)}史上最強！的辣味！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.65,0:16:03.59,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,200)}辣                            痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.95,0:16:03.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼辣和痛苦是同一個漢字…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.15,0:16:14.47,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}戀人們想一起看的電影
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.15,0:16:14.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛進行時
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.34,0:16:18.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.89,0:16:23.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家三姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.90,0:00:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.93,0:16:27.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然一個人去看戀愛進行時
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.42,0:16:30.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過超級催淚  很好看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.67,0:16:40.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  利子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.12,0:16:44.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭子  到底怎樣才能傳達自己的心意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.21,0:16:50.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,率直地用語言來表達不就好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.65,0:16:53.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為做不到才問你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.66,0:16:55.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這能算是滿分回答嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.17,0:16:58.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那找他去約會之類的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.49,0:17:03.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有部叫「戀愛進行時」的感人的愛情片  很棒的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.64,0:17:05.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個太難了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.26,0:17:10.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優等生有時候總把很難的事情說的好像很簡單一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.63,0:17:15.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…送點什麼東西之類的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.60,0:17:18.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己親手做的東西說不定能傳達心意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.73,0:17:23.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤岡來的話  圭子也會來的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.80,0:17:24.46,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親手做的…禮物？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.21,0:17:25.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.15,0:17:27.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那下次就來我家開學習會咯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.32,0:17:29.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了嗎  圭子  利子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.96,0:17:38.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該做什麼來當禮物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.18,0:17:40.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選什麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.01,0:17:44.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在戀愛進行時裏是手織的圍巾哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.39,0:17:47.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己織圍巾傳達過頭了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.79,0:17:50.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太沉重的會讓對方受不了的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.79,0:17:53.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也就想起來這麼一說而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.21,0:17:56.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那點心之類的應該不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.42,0:17:58.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃掉之後也不會留下些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.77,0:17:59.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,點心嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.14,0:18:02.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餅乾之類的可以選在大家聚在一起的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.73,0:18:04.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也比較容易送出手…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.11,0:18:05.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧克力之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.32,0:18:07.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  情人節還太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.58,0:18:11.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做蛋糕  然後切給大家的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.99,0:18:14.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個也不行  會露餡的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.98,0:18:17.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了！餅乾的話！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.17,0:18:20.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他絕對能吃到一塊的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.47,0:18:23.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  就決定是餅乾了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.67,0:18:24.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.97,0:18:29.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就說是餅乾了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.85,0:18:36.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想做得好還是按食譜做比較放心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.65,0:18:44.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,低筋麵粉200克  無鹽黃油120克  食鹽少許
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.59,0:18:47.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少許是指多少啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.17,0:18:51.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭子  你覺得少許應該是多少
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.62,0:18:53.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點點？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.76,0:18:56.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一點點又是多少？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.59,0:18:59.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一點點就好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.28,0:19:02.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是多少？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.34,0:19:04.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子有一點餓了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.10,0:19:05.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是多少？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.52,0:19:08.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意外地神經質呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.33,0:19:14.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點點到底是多少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.50,0:19:20.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利子  你是不是洗手洗太久…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.60,0:19:27.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒聽到呢  真是神經質呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.42,0:19:34.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤岡同學在哭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.99,0:19:36.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.68,0:19:38.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先拿出手帕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.22,0:19:44.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  今天帶的手帕是早上熨過最喜歡的那塊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.44,0:19:46.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是剛才已經用過了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.32,0:19:48.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能把濕的手帕給別人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.20,0:19:50.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤岡怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.84,0:19:51.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來手帕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.51,0:19:53.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.18,0:19:56.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.90,0:19:58.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是眼睛裏進了一點點沙子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.00,0:20:01.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  常有的事  眼睛偶爾也會進點沙子的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.00,0:20:07.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  雖然無意間拒絕了她的手帕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.11,0:20:09.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也讓我失去了明天把手帕洗乾淨還給她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.97,0:20:12.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個能和南同學說話的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.01,0:20:14.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是有一點後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.86,0:20:19.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  現在又好像很消沉的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.70,0:20:29.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從昨天開始就有那麼一點點困
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.35,0:20:32.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是所謂的春眠不覺曉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.18,0:20:33.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是秋天  而且還是下午
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.01,0:20:36.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你全弄錯了  蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.20,0:20:38.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下是真的困了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.30,0:20:40.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能睡一會麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.00,0:20:41.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.78,0:20:44.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說餅乾算是完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.82,0:20:46.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還是很在意鹽的份量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.31,0:20:49.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是不要拿出來好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.18,0:20:55.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從利子那邊傳來一點點甜甜的香味
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.76,0:21:00.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是在說這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.50,0:21:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那麼一點點好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.95,0:21:14.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然比春香姐姐做的有那麼一點點遜色
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.80,0:21:16.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也還不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.55,0:21:18.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就別吃嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.08,0:21:29.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.96,0:21:38.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了那一點點甜甜的香味
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.33,0:21:40.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓藤岡同學吃到我的餅乾了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.17,0:21:43.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  我要小小地感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.82,0:21:45.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到我的想法的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.18,0:21:47.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能再多一點咸味就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.72,0:21:48.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到底是多少啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.90,0:00:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
